org.eclipse.scada.configuration.component.exec

Interface ExecComponentsPackage

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ExecComponentsPackageImpl

    public interface ExecComponentsPackage
    The Package for the model. It contains accessors for the meta objects to represent
    • each class,
    • each feature of each class,
    • each operation of each class,
    • each enum,
    • and each data type
    Reports system information using "vmstat".
    See Also:
    ExecComponentsFactory
